nafiir = Sudanese Ar. group work, collective work. as in many areas of the Sudan the group work is very common in sudanese society. for example if you have something to do you can call as many as possible people who would come and help you, like in farming, building a house, cleaning, harvesting and the like. Even the government somtimes resort to such collective work to build public services institution like hospitals, schools , mosques, and staduims
